Third-party components
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This repository builds the GEMC documentation website. It is generated with
Jekyll and embeds third-party web assets (for example, the VTK.js viewer used to
display interactive geometry scenes) that are separately licensed. Such
components are provided under their respective licenses, and you must comply
with those licenses in addition to the Apache License, Version 2.0 that covers
the GEMC documentation content itself.

